made by Credit Card or PayPal. Once you have completed the purchase, your account will instantly be updated to allow the multi-website feature.</p>\n<p>If you already have a multiple website account and would like to only scan a single website weekly, this is free of charge, however you will need to <a title="Sign up for a WebsiteDefender account" href="https://dashboard.websitedefender.com/register-for-free-website-scan.php">create a new WebsiteDefender account</a>. This step must be carried out in order for your service to continue without interruption. From  1<sup>st</sup> March 2012, beta users who are scanning multiple websites will no longer be able to secure them without a WebsiteDefender Subscription, as their accounts will be deactivated.</p>\n<p>For any questions regarding a WebsiteDefender Pricing Plan, please contact <a title="The WebsiteDefender Sales Team" href="mailto:sales@websitedefender.com">sales@websitedefender.com</a>.</p>\n<p>Stay Secure!</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:135:"http://www.websitedefender.com/announcements/websitedefender-news/websitedefender-multi-site-edition-approaching-official-release/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}}}s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:1:{s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:3:{s:4:"href";s:36:"http://www.websitedefender.com/feed/";s:3:"rel";s:4:"self";s:4:"type";s:19:"application/rss+xml";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:44:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/";a:2:{s:12:"updateP