(78134, 'wsd_feed_data', 'O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:7:"expires";i:1331976258;s:4:"data";s:3850:"<ul><li><h4><a href="http://www.websitedefender.com/web-security/web-application-security-breach/" target="_blank" title="Posted on March 14, 2012 | 2:51 pm">Web Security Tip of the Week: What Constitutes a Web Application Security Breach?</a></h4><p>A web application security breach means different things to different people. To some it could mean having attacker <a href="http://www.websitedefender.com/web-security/web-application-security-breach/" target="_blank" title="Read all article">[...]</a></p></li><li><h4><a href="http://www.websitedefender.com/web-security/what-exactly-is-web-malware/" target="_blank" title="Posted on March 9, 2012 | 4:17 pm">Web Security Tip of the Week: What Exactly is Web Malware?</a></h4><p>Since 1984, the word “virus” was used to describe what we now call malware. Malware is short for malicious soft <a href="http://www.websitedefender.com/web-security/what-exactly-is-web-malware/" target="_blank" title="Read all article">[...]</a></p></li><li><h4><a href="http://www.websitedefender.com/web-security/eliminating-wordpress-security-risks/" target="_blank" title="Posted on March 7, 2012 | 3:46 pm">Eliminating WordPress Security Risks</a></h4><p>According to a study by Geek Estate, 14.7% of the entire web (top one million sites) is running on WordPress, with  <a href="http://www.websitedefender.com/web-security/eliminating-wordpress-security-risks/" target="_blank" title="Read all article">[...]</a></p></li><li><h4><a href="http://www.websitedefender.com/web-security/websitedefender-account-credentials-security-check/" target="_blank" title="Posted on February 29, 2012 | 3:34 pm">WebsiteDefender security check: Verifying your account credentials ensures website security</a></h4><p>Website security is like physical security. From barricades and building surveillance in the physical realm to soft <a href="http://www.websitedefender.com/web-security/websitedefender-account-credentials-security-check/" target="_blank" title="Read all article">[...]</a></p></li><li><h4><a href="http://www.websitedefender.com/announcements/websitedefender-news/websitedefender-multi-site-edition-approaching-official-release/" target="_blank" title="Posted on February 22, 2012 | 4:07 pm">The WebsiteDefender Multi-Site Edition Approaching Official Release</a></h4><p>The next stage in the evolution of Acunetix’s WebsiteDefender has arrived highlighting significant improvements i <a href="http://www.websitedefender.com/announcements/websitedefender-news/websitedefender-multi-site-edition-approaching-official-release/" target="_blank" title="Read all article">[...]</a></p></li></ul><div style="border-top: solid 1px #ccc; margin-top: 4px; padding: 2px 0;"><p style="margin: 5px 0 0 0; padding: 0 0; line-height: normal; overflow: hidden;"><a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/Websitedefendercom"\n                                style="float: left; display: block; width: 50%; text-align: right; margin-left: 30px;\n                                padding-right: 22px; background: url(http://creditbox.info/wp-content/plugins/secure-wordpress/img/rss.png) no-repeat right center;"\n                                target="_blank">Follow us on RSS</a><a href="#" id="wsd_close_rss_widget"\n                                style="float: right; display: block; width: 16px; height: 16px;\n                                margin: 0 0; background: url(http://creditbox.info/wp-content/plugins/secure-wordpress/img/close-button.png) no-repeat 0 0;"\n                                    title="Close widget"></a><form id="wsd_form" method="post"></form></p><script type="text/javascript">\n                    document.getElementById("wsd_close_rss_widget").onclick = function(){\n                            document.getElementById("wsd_form").submit();\n                        };\n                </script></div>";}', 'yes'),
(78914, 'exchangers_tabletext', 'a:1:{s:6:"before";s:1291:"Для получения более подробных данных о работе выбранного кредитного сервиса установите указатель мышки на иконке <img title="Подробнее" src="/wp-content/plugins/credit-automats-monitor/images/info.png" alt="Подробнее" width="22" height="15" />, расположенной слева от названия автомата. В таблице звездочкой <img title="Новичок" src="/wp-content/plugins/credit-automats-monitor/images/star.png" alt="Новичок" width="16" height="16" /> отмечены новые кредитные автоматы. С помощью закладки "Настройки" <img title="Закладка &quot;Настройки&quot;" src="/wp-content/plugins/credit-automats-monitor/images/config.png" alt="Закладка &quot;Настройки&quot;" width="12" height="12" /> можно изменять валюту кредита WMZ, WMR,WME или WMU. Ответы на самые актуальные вопросы Вы можете найти в разделах <a href="/wiki/">Wiki словарик</a> словарик и <a href="/faq/" target="_blank">FAQ</a> в верхнем меню "Помощь".";}', 'yes'),
